==Adjective==
<b>Idiocy</b>
#The state of being an idiot, as if one is unintelligent.
<i>Well, that person there is a fine example of idiocy...<i>

==Popular Usage==
The word 'idiocy' appears in the dictionary on [[w:The Simpsons|The Simpsons]] under the definition of "Pull a Homer" - to succeed despite idiocy.